sources.title: Rainbow's End (1935) HOOT GIBSON
sources.description:
Stars: Hoot Gibson, June Gale, Oscar Apfel
Director: Norval Spencer

A rancher's son finds himself helping another rancher who is at odds with his father--all because of the father's crooked partner.

metadata.Plot: Losing a barroom brawl, the unconscious Gibson and Kendall are put on a train heading west where they get jobs on Ware's ranch. There they get involved with Ware's fight against Stark, the man who just happens to be the crooked partner of Gibson's father.
metadata.Actors: Hoot Gibson, June Gale, Oscar Apfel
